reviewText: A great concert in a great blu-ray the aditional material is very good, very different to the dvd version, the presentation is good

Nice concert, most of the old good songs are here and the new ones too, quality is very good. Something that I don't quite understand is the second disc it has some kind of documentary and has static images along with the audio of the concert that is in the first disc. Anyway is a good buy for any Indochine fan
